                     <interp inst="t18220220-173-person1599" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a furrier, between eight and half-past eight o'clock, I saw the prisoner going up the prosecutor's stairs - he came out with the roller under his arm. I knew him before.</p>
