            . I am a watchman. About a quarter past ten o'clock at night, I found the roller in Ship-court, against a wall.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. The place is so dark you cannot see your hand before you.</p>
